stork.feather.util

Class AnonymousSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • stork.feather.Session<AnonymousSession,AnonymousResource>
      • stork.feather.util.AnonymousSession

  • public class AnonymousSession
extends Session<AnonymousSession,AnonymousResource>
    A base class for anonymous Sessions. AnonymousSessions and AnonymousResources are generally used for creating virtual Sinks and Taps that emit Slices that aren't based on real addressable Resources, yet must declare an associated Resource to work within the framework. This class represents a virtual Session such implementations may use.
